body:
Hello my dear Avicans,

So within the space of 4 days I reached 24 subscribers. I have received so much positive feedback. So I would now like to thank you. Thank you for supporting me and helping me out.

So when I pass 30 subscribers I will be giving away an Avatar.

NOTE: The winner will get to choose it with or without text

Click here to go to my Youtube channel

---------------------------------------------

How to enter...

Entering is simple, just subscribe to my channel and then comment below your Youtube channel, be honest and don't lie about subscribing.

Should I unsubscribe after the giveaway...

Well that is in your power, but if you would like to support me please stay subscribed.
